# E-Commerce Platform

## Product

An online store. Customers browse products, add to cart, checkout, and track orders.

## What the User Sees

### Screen: Product Page

+------------------------------------------+
|  [Logo]  Shop  Categories  Cart(3)       |
|------------------------------------------|
|                                          |
|  [Product Image]                         |
|                                          |
|  Wireless Headphones               $79   |
|  4.2 stars (128 reviews)                 |
|  [Add to Cart]                           |
+------------------------------------------+

